Pre-Requisite:

1)Hadoop Installation (Guide available at Bigdata/InstallationGuide)
2)Hive Installation (Guide available at Bigdata/HiveGuide)

Procedure:

Download the raw data available at MovieAnalysis/rawdata
The data is available in unparsed(may contain bad records too).

So we need to parse the data to correct form and eliminated bad records
The code for the same is available at Movie Analysis/code/parse/

Then, we can load data to hive for easily querying
The code is available inside hive repository (Movie Analysis/code/Hive)

For calculating Average rating of each genre for each age group and each profession
the code is available at Genre Rank by Age and Genre Rank by Profession repositories
